; Lift print head a bit
G1 Z50.2 ; Move print head up

G1 X0 Y210 F7200
G1 E2 F5000
G1 E2 F5500
G1 E2 F6000
G1 E-15.0000 F5800
G1 E-20.0000 F5500
G1 E10.0000 F3000
G1 E-10.0000 F3100
G1 E10.0000 F3150
G1 E-10.0000 F3250
G1 E10.0000 F3300


M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan

; Unload filament
M702 C

G4 ; wait
M221 S100 ; reset flow
M900 K0 ; reset LA
M907 E538 ; reset extruder motor current
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M73 P100 R0
M73 Q100 S0
G1 X0 Y210 F3000 ; home X axis
M84 ; disable motors
M73 P100 R0
M73 Q100 S0
